lead_paragraph: Donald Trump wants his name taken off two Atlantic City, New Jersey, casinos he founded but no longer controls, saying in a lawsuit that they have become so dilapidated that they damage his brand image.

headline.main: Donald Trump Sues to Strip His Name From NJ Casinos in 'Disrepair'
